{"tid":1438420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人加油","createTime":"2019-08-09T18:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T19:49:52.000Z","uid":226602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3384edba6a776449c920d3ec8bfe80faf639c332","tid":1438420,"uid":226602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:17:53.000Z","msg":"堅定意志係好難嘅事，唔好將啲小事咩黑警呀何君堯呢啲狗屎垃圾放喺心度，佢地唔做共慘黨奴才都大把人會做，呢啲賤種唔值得我地一提。<br />\n收回惡法，港人治港，高度自治，真普選，拎返我地二十幾年所漸漸失去既野，對準港共政權，唔好分化，光復香港，時代革命。我信香港人。"},{"pid":"d5c688fe4497e42b948d2dcc96793ec0ad92bed4","tid":1438420,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:46:41.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n香港人重點日程：<br />\n8月9-11日：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)<br />\n8月10日：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n8月10日：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n8月10日：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）<br />\n8月11日：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n8月11日：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFF4YRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFF4YRE.jpg&h=539785ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9Lc7Li.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9Lc7Li.jpg&h=8d1626e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFLHLw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFLHLw8.jpg&h=d8fae00a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYaMsLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxYaMsLz.jpg&h=b4f4136d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CH1PqYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCH1PqYA.jpg&h=5a975883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQEdSDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQEdSDA.jpg&h=da0e19d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/276scxO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F